    <bf:summary>
      <bf:Summary>
	<rdfs:label>"When Harriet Barnes is found gulty of murder by a jury chaired by Roger Collins, Harriet swears vengeance on the Collins family - then kills herself. Soon Celia Dalton, a guest at Collinwood, starts suffering strange spells. And each time, someone at Collinwood is violently attacked"--Container.</rdfs:label>
      </bf:Summary>
    </bf:summary>
